snippet.title: Kitty May Cry - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam：https://store.steampowered.com/app/2123100/

Kitty May Cry is a 3D open world adventure-puzzle game in which you take on the role of a black kitty cat, stranded upon a little island chock-full of ancient relics thanks to a failed rocket launch. Hunt down your lost backpack and the batteries now scattered across the land.
